30051254.description: With this killer Maxi Dress in your fashion arsenal, In Any Event, you'll have all the power you will ever need. Your frenemies will fall to their knees in fits of jealousy, and you will be able to laugh (on the inside of course, you are a lady after all). You will twirl about the dance floor, enjoying the feel of the rhythm in your bones, and the looks of envy you'll be getting from everyone else who glances your way. Some will compliment you, some will ask you where you got your attire, and some will just stare slack-jawed. You can wink at those last folks. They tend to wilt on contact. Maxi dress features a v-neckline and adjustable straps that cross an open back. Dress has a mesh overlay decorated with flocked velvet flowers. Dress has an invisible back zipper with single hook and eye closure.__Model is wearing a small._¢Â100% Polyester_¢Â_and wash cold_¢Â_ined_¢Â_mported

31973542.description: If you wanna look as sassy and chic as me, Walk This Way and grab this gorgeous high-low floral print dress for yourself! You won_ regret the investment. There_ nothing about this lovely arrangement of colors and fabric that you won_ love and adore. 55527549.description: Feel like wishing on a star? How about a Midwest Shooting Star? Then wish on me while I_ wearing this sassy little sequin number, because that_ what it_ called, and it_ every bit as pretty as a wishing star. Plus you never know_t might have the power to grant wishes. I wished that it would make me look fabulous and it does! Black fitted dress features a v-neckline, short sleeves, a deep v-cut back with thick straps across, and an abundance of silver beading and red, silver and blue sequins in a geometric striped pattern. Dress features an invisible side zipper and double waist darts in front and back. Model is wearing a small.  100% Polyester  Hand Wash Cold  Lined  Imported

57523933.description: Even if you_e not going out for a Night At The Met, you can still look the part with this incredible maxi dress. After all, why should everyone who gets to go get to have all the fun? And of course, if you are going for a night there, this would be the perfect dress for that as well. Nonetheless, this beauty is a dress to write home about. So get out your pens ladies, and start scribing (or laptop, you know, if you_e not into the whole retro thing)._This stunning tulle dress features a high halter neckline, lace halter tie straps, a ruched bodice, an empire waist, and floral eyelash lace trim._ Maxi dress features a three tiered skirt with swiss dot tulle, floral embroidered tulle, and plain tulle. Skirt layers are trimmed with fine plastic mesh to provide structure._ Dress has an invisible back zipper topped with a hook and eye closure, princess seams, and lower waist darts in front and back. Model is wearing a small. ¢Â100% Polyester  Hand Wash Cold  Lined  Imported

63454933.description: You saw it in his eyes when you glided into the room wearing this gorgeously chic_lace dress. He'll never be the same now that you've taken his heart. He will Want You To Stay and never leave his side. Not hidden behind him, not shoved in front of him, but by his side. You two were made for each other, kinda like me and you, right? He's one lucky man. And you're one lucky lady to have both me (the perfect lace dress) and the handsome man. This is the kind of story fairy tales are written about, don't you agree? This elegant lace dress features a tunic silhouette, double v-necklines, and a scalloped hem. Model is wearing an x-small.  60% Cotton 30% Nylon 10% Rayon  Hand Wash Cold  Lined: 100% Cotton  Imported

63483789.description: When prepping for that hot date, every detail has to be meticulously accounted for. Hair, carefully styled to give the impression of being nonchalantly tousled, makeup just subtle enough that it looks like you don't even need the stuff, shoes that are not only to die for, but that perfectly align your posture, and, the most important part, the dress. And if you really want to Dot Your I's, then nothing less than this dress will do. DaVinci, eat your heart out, because nothing tops you, you work of art you. Elegant dress features a plunging V neck on a fitted, ruching bodice, adjustable criss cross spaghetti straps, chiffon overlay, and double slit skirt with an invisible zipper closure in back. Model is wearing a small._¢Â100% Polyester_¢Â_and Wash Cold_¢Â_ined_¢Â_mported

65333434.description: If you Could Stop Time and hold this moment for forever, would you? The second you saw me, you knew I would be your only maxi dress for this day. I am perfect for you not just today but all summer long. Flowy, gorgeous, graceful, all the things you need in a dress: I have them. We can make every day you wear me be as heavenly as this one. Whether we're at the beach, on an island, by the lake, or in the mountains, we will be stunning together. Now, put the time turner down and let's get back to enjoying regularly scheduled life! This elegant sleeveless maxi dress features a_smocked flounced bodice, an invisible back zipper, tie straps, and a tiered flowy skirt. 74487836.description: Sleek and streamlined, this leather wallet bag is both superhandy (the divided compartments are big enough for an iPhone Plus) and supercool (the adjustable chain strap can be worn crossbody or doubled up as a top handle). Functional and fuss-free-this is the way we do a going-out purse.
74487836.details: Made of semi vegetable-tanned leather with a softly worn waxed finish that deepens into a distinctive patina. Please note: As it is made of a natural material, each bag varies slightly in texture and color. Stud closure. Slip pocket. 21 5/8" crossbody drop. 5 1/8"H x 6 1/2"W x 2 3/8"D. Import.

84823874.description: Darling! You didn't warn me that you would be dressed all femme fatal this evening. Lawt have mercy! You are a siren walking in that dazzling lace dress. No one will be able to resist your charms. Wait. You're taken, you say? By that cool drink of water over there? Whew! I was about to send out a warning to all your friends to lock up their main squeezes. Well, if your man hasn't fallen at your feet before now, he will tonight. You are sensational in that high-low lacy gown, my dear, just ravishing! This luscious lace dress features a halter neckline, and an open back with zipper cutting down it. Dress features a dramatic high-low hemline. Model is wearing a small.  65% Cotton 35% Nylon  Hand Wash Cold  Lined to Mid Thigh: 95% Polyester 5% Spandex  Imported

88918251.description: I'm telling you this dress Flirts With Love, not just "like". No, this lovely little number steals the show when you put it on. You are going to fall head over tip toes in love with this dress. No one else has a chance to look as fun and flirty as you do while wearing it. And did I mention how very comfy it is? No? Well, girl, it's definitely right up there on the easy-breezy scale. The fuss and non-sense of other dresses isn't even a concern. Just chic style and all the fun times rolled into this darling! What are you waiting for? Make it yours before it's gone! This chambray dress features a round neckline, short trumpet sleeves, and a ruffled hem. Dress has a back zipper, bust darts, and upper waist darts in front and back. Model is wearing a size 0.  100% Lyocell  Dry Clean Only  Unlined  Imported

88918251.title: Flirts With Love Light Chambray Dress

95163851.description: Globe-trotting Folk Fortune designer Michaela Smeaton creates eco-friendly designs inspired by traditional handicrafts. Woven by Balinese artisans, this round rattan bag has a leather shoulder strap and bold batik lining.
95163851.details: Shoulder strap drop: 21". 8"H x 8"W x 2 1/2"D. Rattan palm straw with leather trim. Button closure. Import. Select stores. ï¿
95163851.title: Folk Fortune Bali Rattan Roundie Bag

96196857.description: Inspired by old-school biker style (and some boyfriends past and present), our signature leather jacket combines buttery soft, pebbled leather with chunky silver hardware. Guaranteed to up the cool quotient of pretty much any outfit. ï¿
96196857.details: True to size. Leather. Professional leather clean. Import.
96196857.title: Ultimate Leather Motorcycle Jacket

97896342.description: Hold on to your hats, ladies and gentlemen, the lovely lady in the show stopping maxi dress is about to Flit On By you. She doesn't walk or trod like the rest of us mortals. No, she floats and flits with an airy grace most of you blokes can never master. The dress she has chosen for today's event gives her a most stunning advantage over any other maxi around, wouldn't you agree? Those layered tiers, the colors of a spring day, and that elegant neckline! Gracious! She will be the talk of the town for years to come, if I do say so myself. This sleeveless maxi dress features a plunging v-neckline, an empire waist giving way to a tiered skirt, and detachable matching belt with buckle. Dress has an invisible back zipper topped with a hook and eye closure. Model is wearing a small.  100% Polyester  Hand Wash Cold  Lined  Imported

99227756.description: When it comes to Matters Of The Heart, a woman really needs to be careful. We're not saying to lock it away in a glass box and only bring it out on special occasions, but the heart is a fragile thing (and surprisingly strong when it needs to be). So in the care and feeding of the heart, one needs to treat it to special things now and then, and when the heart has a sudden urge, a want or longing, we find it's best to give in and splurge. Like if your heart wants this maxi dress, for example (just saying). Elegant dress features a plunging V neck on a fitted, ruching bodice, adjustable criss cross spaghetti straps, mesh overlay, and double slit skirt with an invisible zipper closure in back. Model is wearing a small.  100% Polyester  Hand Wash Cold  Lined  Imported

99617082.description: Made of top-quality leather in timeless shapes, our newest collection is destined for classic status (the vibe = vintage dream bag). Sleek and minimalist, this roomy shoulder bag has a superadjustable strap and space for all your must-carries and then some (read: it's that just-right iPad/book size you've been searching for).
99617082.details: Made of vegetable-tanned leather that burnishes with wear into a beautiful patina. Please note: As it is made of a natural material, each bag varies slightly in texture and color. Magnetic pin closure. 15" shoulder drop (at longest). 7 1/4"H x 10"W. Import.
99617082.title: The Abroad Shoulder Bag

99846682.description: OK handsome, I_e got my maxi dress packed, plane ticket in hand and I want you to Meet Me In Malibu! Or if you_ prefer, we can ditch the expensive trip and we can take a walk in the park (I_ still wearing this dress though) and we can pretend all the same. This lovely garment has me in the mood to enjoy the sun and I_ ready to forget all my worries and focus on today and all the joy in the world. So what do you say? Are you game?_Maxi wrap dress features a v-neckline, and tie waist with an additional inner tie._ Model is wearing a small.  100%_Rayon  Machine Wash Cold  Unlined  Imported
